      "para_id": "Q001522.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Bau , the kind woman , her lady , Ninala , ( Gudea's ) spouse , dedicated this ( bowl ) for the well-being of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , and for her own well-being ."
